snippet.description:
The wait is over.  “VALLE” is here! MATATA teams up with DJAMES for a track packed with infectious energy, unforgettable melodies, and visuals that hit from start to finish. Press play, turn it all the way up, and experience “Valle” the way it was meant to be heard.
MATATA ft. DJAMES – Valle (Official Music Video)



VIDEO CREDITS

Directed by: Matata
Produced by: Collo Milan
Director of Photography (DOP): Tommy
Gaffer: Amund
Edited by: Matata
Color Grade: Zarataski

AUDIO CREDITS

Produced by: DJAMES (@djameskickit )
Guitars: Benjamin Kabaseke & Yvan Kwizera
Mixed & Mastered by: MixedByChopz

